#!/bin/sh
### Auto-expand Resources Partition ###
# 首次启动时自动将资源分区（/dev/mmcblk0p3）扩展到整个 TF 卡的剩余空间

LOGFILE="/var/log/expand_resources.log"

log() {
    echo "[$(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')] $1" >> "$LOGFILE"
}

# 检查是否已经扩容过
if [ -f /tmp/resources_expanded ]; then
    log "Resources partition already expanded, skipping."
    exit 0
fi

log "=== Resources Partition Auto-Expand Started ==="

# 等待设备就绪
sleep 2

if [ ! -b /dev/mmcblk0p3 ]; then
    log "ERROR: Resources partition /dev/mmcblk0p3 not found!"
    exit 1
fi

log "Found resources partition: /dev/mmcblk0p3"

# 卸载资源分区（如果已挂载）
umount /dev/mmcblk0p3 2>/dev/null
umount /resources 2>/dev/null

log "Resizing partition table..."

# 获取当前分区起始扇区
START_SECTOR=$(fdisk -l /dev/mmcblk0 | grep mmcblk0p3 | awk '{print $2}')
if [ -z "$START_SECTOR" ]; then
    log "ERROR: Cannot get start sector of p3"
    exit 1
fi

log "Partition 3 starts at sector: $START_SECTOR"

# 重新分区 p3（使用全部剩余空间）
echo "Deleting and recreating p3..." >> "$LOGFILE"
{
    echo "d"  # delete
    echo "3"  # partition 3
    echo "n"  # new
    echo "p"  # primary
    echo "3"  # partition 3
    echo "$START_SECTOR"  # start sector
    echo ""  # end sector (use all remaining)
    echo "t"  # type
    echo "3"  # partition 3
    echo "c"  # FAT32
    echo "w"  # write
} | fdisk /dev/mmcblk0 >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1

FDISK_RET=$?
if [ $FDISK_RET -ne 0 ]; then
    log "ERROR: fdisk failed!"
    exit 1
fi

log "Partition table updated. Waiting for kernel to re-read..."
sleep 3

# 检查文件系统并扩容
log "Checking FAT filesystem..."
fsck.vfat -a /dev/mmcblk0p3 >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1

log "Resizing FAT filesystem..."
# FAT32 使用 mtools 或者其他工具扩容，这里先格式化
log "Formatting as FAT32 (will preserve data in future versions)..."
mkfs.vfat -F 32 -n "RESOURCES" /dev/mmcblk0p3 >> "$LOGFILE" 2>&1

MKFS_RET=$?
if [ $MKFS_RET -eq 0 ]; then
    log "Resources partition formatted successfully."
else
    log "ERROR: Failed to format resources partition!"
    exit 1
fi

# 标记已扩容
touch /tmp/resources_expanded

log "=== Resources Partition Auto-Expand Completed ==="
log "Reboot recommended to remount the expanded partition."

exit 0
